data.title: The Bronze Buckaroo Rides Off Into The Sunset
data.meta_description: The black singing cowboy Herb Jeffries sang a Duke Ellington hit and appeared in 1930s westerns like Harlem Rides the Range and The Bronze Buckaroo.
